      "seed": 1644040516,
      "version": 410,
      "versionNonce": 198959428,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772803525724,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "The same goes for the guard, if\nthey then continue their\npattern after being interrupted,\nthe other guard notices and\ngoes to have a look. They'll\nrealise it's the guard but get a\nbit more suspicious",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "qEMVlzEt_hDYNh36yYCb4",
      "originalText": "The same goes for the guard, if they then continue their pattern after being interrupted, the other guard notices and goes to have a look. They'll realise it's the guard but get a bit more suspicious",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
