      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Guards should maintain\na suspicion log, which\nshould record the type\nof suspicion, e.g too\nloud, broken object,\noccurance count, and\nlast occurance.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "fkA7IWABwnzHf1N6qUkmQ",
      "originalText": "Guards should maintain a suspicion log, which should record the type of suspicion, e.g too loud, broken object, occurance count, and last occurance.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
