      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "_F6ByAWSk_ewvoCkUlv2C",
      "originalText": "They should try and stick to a schedule for movement on their route, hitting nodes.",
