      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "qd3VGFj4_Lmqe643UZD2d",
      "originalText": "If interrupted, they should try and gradually return back to their expected times. They should track schedule drift and try and gradually \n",
