      "updated": 1772803583724,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Guards with schedule drift\nfrom interruption will inform\nother guards of it when\ninvestigated, who will remember\nand not investigate them for a\nbit.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "bYSHI8E07FpIbU-VrNSfd",
      "originalText": "Guards with schedule drift from interruption will inform other guards of it when investigated, who will remember and not investigate them for a bit.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
