      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Excuses.\nYou should be able to find items\nthat, if caught, give you an\nexcusable reason to be there.\ne.g important looking documents\n(the guard will take them and\nask you to leave the restricted\narea).\ne.g",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "aeXCAH507DRVOAnM8Ei-X",
      "originalText": "Excuses.\nYou should be able to find items that, if caught, give you an excusable reason to be there.\ne.g important looking documents (the guard will take them and ask you to leave the restricted area).\ne.g",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
